  "body": "<h1>Oxidizing Lightning Rods</h1>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a>\n</strong></p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This Fabric mod makes it possible for you to oxidize lightning rods. The lightning rods oxidize over time and you can wax them at any stage you want. All you need to do is to craft the normal lightning rod and it will oxidize over time.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Individual oxidation stages look this:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2fuO91v.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"567\" height=\"239\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<center><a href=\"https://shorturl.at/nTUW6\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FQLov3P.png\" alt=\"Use Code marstheplanet at https://www.bisecthosting.com/marstheplanet\" width=\"500\"/>\n</a></center>",
